Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:12.45,Sign,,0,0,0,,This animation work was based on experiences shared with us by the readers. {この作品は皆さまから寄せられた体験談をアニメ化したものです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Human life is ever so fleeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When lingering regrets won't let some depart this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,they're forced to wander \Nthe Earth for years to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"I witnessed a wandering spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:35.50,Sign,,0,0,0,,School Ghosts {学校の幽霊}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A first-hand account of horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.34,0:00:45.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,Kagoshima Prefecture "S" Junior High School
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:47.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,Music room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.34,0:01:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already dark outside, you should go hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's that late already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.65,0:01:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I got carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.34,0:01:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're always studying until late?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.39,0:01:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I have a test coming up.\NI was at a sick leave for quite a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.08,0:01:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out this late may worry your mother. C'mon, hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm cutting the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:58.59,Sign,,0,0,0,,Forgotten Notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I forgot my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.82,0:02:56.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,Mourning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept my sincerest condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was me who told her to hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And she forgot this notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What a truly hard working,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,fair young lady she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with the custodian? {nc whats the last word}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:10.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,A few months later
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is someone still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,T-There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 2 A.M. already,..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just the pump?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! She's returned! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,God! Buddha! Save me! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,S-S-Someone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,God, Buddha... G-God, Buddha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.18,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God save us all, God save us all... {Namu Amida Butsu}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,God... Buddha... God... Buddha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it through?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Batting Ghost
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:09:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This strange phenomenon started about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time it happened was when students who were going home late
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,from preparing for the school festival tried to take a shortcut across the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,the school was rife with rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,either of someone standing still, or someone knocking a ball on the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What they saw was the ghost of Nagao-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Next one's to the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.89,0:09:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After Nagao-sensei became the baseball team's new coach,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,they had a streak of victories
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.23,0:10:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and now even dared to dream about playing at Koshien.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting with the team itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone from fellow student to the PTA were setting their hopes high.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, the third batter Matsumoto-kun fell into a slump
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and was scored with 30 no-hitters in a row. {unsure if thats how it works but can't be bothered to learn baseball terminology}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nagao-sensei refused to change the batting order or team members,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.72,0:10:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,expecting that Matsumoto-kun was going to start hitting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumor has it, it happened two weeks before an important game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Nagao-sensei,\Ncan we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to drag the rest of the team down any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to retire from being the third batter. {because the third one is considered among the most important}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.74,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hit anymore, I want to quit baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.97,0:10:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't quit over the smallest hurdle, you dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagao-sensei encouraged Matsumoto-kun and took him to the batter box.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, swing the bat. Swing! I said swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.96,0:11:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Lower your head, tuck the chin in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.53,0:11:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? Why'd you stop? Swing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.67,0:11:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto, toss for me and look closely to understand what you're doing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You can hit it, you have what it takes to be a batter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All you need to do is swing more confidently.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, keep tossing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.80,0:11:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,After about five more minutes of doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.14,0:11:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-kun fumbled the ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, the bat that Nagao-sensei swung hit Matsumoto in the back of his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They got an ambulance for him at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Matsumoto-kun was paralyzed from the waist down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The faculty treated this as an incident of bullying by teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.07,0:12:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The media and PTAs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.24,0:12:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,unleashed a storm of criticism on Nagao-sensei's teaching methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And because he had a stronger than usual sense of responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.84,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a few days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he committed suicide by hanging himself on a branch of the sakura tree
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in the far corner of the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei's death was a shock to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But even more shocking
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,was that his ghost then started silently prowling the campus every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,As the manager of the baseball team,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I visited Matsumoto-senpai many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:13:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to persuade him that we need to pacify sensei's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:06.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto Alcohol Store {松本}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.32,0:13:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't hold a grudge against Nagao-sensei or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All I want is to sooner forget the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.36,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I really need to pacify sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said before, teacher's spirit comes to campus every night,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.63,0:13:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,puts his hands together and hangs himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need another reminder of what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My feelings won't change, no matter how many times you ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.79,0:13:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Nagao-sensei appears every night because he wants to apologize to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I don't believe in that kind of stuff! \NIt's nonsense. It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then come and see for yourself whether it's real or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No ghost ever appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.30,0:13:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we go already?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.50,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that..?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei! Nagao-sensei! Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, that's enough! It wasn't your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep my spirits up, even in a wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to feel guilty! \NStop this already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagao-sensei! It's me, Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough! In all this time, I never regretted
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,playing baseball with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So please... Stop condemning yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagao-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.75,0:15:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the sightings of Nagao-sensei's ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.90,0:16:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But every year, when the Sakura tree blossoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the baseball team gathers under that tree to offer their prayers. {/hold a service}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:32.99,Sign,,0,0,0,,Cursed Summer Camp {呪われた夏合宿}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:39.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,Kanagawa Prefecture "S" Girls' High School \NSummer of 1989
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Go ahead, pass it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{generic cheering}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:43.86,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{no idea}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.37,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today's practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.79,0:16:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, it's getting late, so wrap up the cooling down exercises and clean up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.42,0:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you turn on the light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.42,0:17:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I think it's around half past nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope mom recorded the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think everyone is a little too excited for the first day of training camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. I thought so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, that was spooky.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.02,0:17:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who turned off the light?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.52,0:17:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it was just our senpai's prank. Let's head back to the dorms now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pitch dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a baaad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk in that tone, \Nyou're totally creeping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez you're a scaredy-cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:17:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A cat?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew school was no place to come at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If you weren't so sluggish, we wouldn't be here! {no clue what she says here}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Captain and Imai-senpai saw it last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.14,0:18:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I'm not listening to any that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.50,0:18:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just make that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No I didn't! Are you trying to scare me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not! I really heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry back to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, is it true you saw a ghost last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not true, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.37,0:18:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I did see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A long time ago, this school was...\NA hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it was covered in blood, or missing a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The ghost I saw was a nurse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I really need to go to the bathroom. Hey, Chiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten it yet... {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.67,0:19:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Don't wake me up, Kana.\NI was just about to try a scrumptious cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.20,0:19:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, let's go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Come with me. I'm too scared to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh geez, you're hopeless...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:20:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me. Are you still out there? You're there, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you leave without me, Chiko! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure, waiting... {same}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.83,0:20:30.72,Song,,0,0,0,,You may pass now, you may pass, \Nhere on this narrow road... {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/T%C5%8Dryanse}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.82,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out! Stop singing something so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of song would you like, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Chiko you big jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't help it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.44,0:20:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.58,0:20:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.45,0:20:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like it's coming from down the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A wheelchair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.92,0:21:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's a... N-N-N-N-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,N-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A nurse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She came!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,S-She's heading this way! Let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way, I can't move. My legs won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta run now, Kana!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.61,0:21:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! Something's wrong! {lit: here strange}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts... {is that fucking griffith}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here! Here! Here! {lit: it came out/showed up}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.01,0:23:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me water...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai! Captain! Help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here! Here! {same}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.30,0:23:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Painful...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Water...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:32.84,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Please, water...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:56.47,Sign,,0,0,0,,Night on a School Trip
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A school trip is the event of highest magnitude in a high school student's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.08,0:24:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukari spent the trip clutching onto the karaoke mic and posing as a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.79,0:24:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We happily followed our scheduled events for the first, second, and third day,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.42,0:24:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and made it safely to our final stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.94,0:24:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've found your rooms, ask Nakai-san to show you around. {doesnt make no sense idk really}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.07,0:24:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Suzuki and the other girls from the third group will stay in the Blue Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.08,0:24:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.59,0:24:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.59,0:24:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sensei, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.36,0:25:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. There's no other way, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.06,0:25:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Third group's room has been changed from Blue to the Pure Room. {the exact name is 妙浄の間 but 妙浄 (myoujou) is not a real word or a proper name so idk what to make of it, there's a buddhist term that goes joumyou / 浄妙 and means "exquisite purity/perfectly cleansed" so either that or "Myojo Room"}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.83,0:25:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nice detached room.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.80,0:25:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you say Pure Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.27,0:25:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.04,0:25:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.91,0:25:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.26,0:25:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Pure Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.30,0:25:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.20,0:25:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so lucky to get a detached room just for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.27,0:25:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the VIP guests here!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.88,0:25:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,True, true!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.80,0:25:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make all the noise we want!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.81,0:26:01.81,Sign,,0,0,0,,Pure Room {妙浄の間}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.49,0:26:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's a nice room!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.46,0:26:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.86,0:26:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.09,0:26:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you can see the ocean from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.77,0:26:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.00,0:26:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What a room! You can tell it's detached.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.84,0:26:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.84,0:26:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it smell a bit musty in here? And that stain over there looks like a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.34,0:26:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? Doesn't look like one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.35,0:26:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? But I totally see a face there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.85,0:26:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we open the windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.23,0:26:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.60,0:26:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.47,0:26:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.76,0:26:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.86,0:26:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't open because it's nailed down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.77,0:26:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't we allowed to open the windows?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.04,0:26:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.68,0:27:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've prepared tea, dinner will be served in the hall of the main building at 7. {... at the ground floor ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.04,0:27:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{Okay...}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.18,0:27:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai-san, sorry to ask, but could you take a picture for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.04,0:27:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.49,0:27:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good with a camera, s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.06,0:27:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.53,0:27:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that made-up excuse? {lit: that was rude}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.43,0:27:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.20,0:27:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever. We'll use the timer. Gather up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.57,0:27:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, hurry up! Right here! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.78,0:27:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,After dinner, Yukari said she was unwell and went to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.79,0:27:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Yukari, we're going to the baths.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.29,0:27:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame, I knew you wanted to try the open-air bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.03,0:27:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't go calling Sanada-kun while we're not around, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.90,0:27:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.\NI thought I'd just get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.29,0:27:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.53,0:27:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.59,0:28:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.90,0:28:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot, so hot in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.99,0:28:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.50,0:28:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{no idea}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.25,0:29:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.37,0:29:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Join us... {lit: come}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.67,0:29:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.77,0:29:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Join us...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.52,0:29:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.85,0:29:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.70,0:29:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is... calling for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.74,0:29:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Join us...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.62,0:29:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go. Everyone is calling for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.71,0:30:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I can't open it! I mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.23,0:30:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Join us...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.44,0:30:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Yukari?! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.03,0:30:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.50,0:30:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We explained to teacher what happened\N and asked for another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.31,0:30:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, morning came without incident
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.41,0:30:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and we left the ominous inn behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.11,0:30:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, it was really difficult for us to believe Yukari's story.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.75,0:31:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But when we looked at that photo, a chill went down everyone's spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.36,0:31:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.70,0:31:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It was much later when I found out
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.27,0:31:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that the cliffs below the detached building we stayed in
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.40,0:31:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,were famous among locals as the place where those who died at sea
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.64,0:31:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,would often wash up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.88,0:31:37.92,Song,,0,0,0,,In the cage, in the cage, \Na bird is being held {https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kagome_Kagome}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.92,0:31:43.76,Song,,0,0,0,,When, oh when will it come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.76,0:31:49.10,Song,,0,0,0,,In the evening of the dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.10,0:31:53.53,Song,,0,0,0,,The crane and turtle slipped,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.41,0:32:00.08,Song,,0,0,0,,Who is behind you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.80,0:32:08.26,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hanako-san
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.55,0:32:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there was someone at my school named Hanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.28,0:32:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet! You only practice calligraphy when it's quiet, both inside and outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.78,0:32:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.79,0:32:20.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,Flower {Hana}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.80,0:32:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished! It came out nicely this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.34,0:32:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Would be even prettier with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.31,0:32:28.30,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hanako
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.58,0:32:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hanako, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.71,0:32:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.92,0:32:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret it!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.15,0:32:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.38,0:32:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have you all clean the bathrooms as a punishment! {... after school ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.29,0:32:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? No fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.78,0:32:47.80,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hanako
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.67,0:32:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, they say Hanako-san lives in this bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.34,0:33:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The girls from Class 1 saw Hanako-san here!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.58,0:33:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.58,0:33:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true, I heard it directly from one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.35,0:33:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting, let's go meet Hanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.62,0:33:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.12,0:33:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Meet Hanako-san? Sounds fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.89,0:33:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather not...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.56,0:33:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. Hanako-san must be feeling very blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.39,0:33:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,spending her days all alone in this bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.32,0:33:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But they say you shouldn't make fun of Hanako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.70,0:33:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at how scared you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.91,0:33:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, we can't do the cleaning unless we go in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.28,0:33:41.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,Hanako
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.25,0:33:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Which of the doors?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.79,0:33:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The furthermost.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.51,0:33:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is anyone in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.35,0:33:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem so.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.20,0:34:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We've gotta make sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.13,0:34:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who's going to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.94,0:34:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.09,0:34:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Mina. Won't you go knock on the furthermost door?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.91,0:34:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.48,0:34:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't, you're out of our friends' group.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.45,0:34:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,For 5 or 6 years. Or maybe even forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.73,0:34:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,C-C'mon, knock on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.34,0:34:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Just a couple of taps!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.78,0:34:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.29,0:34:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Did anyone answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.42,0:34:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.24,0:34:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Not until we knock more confidently.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.46,0:35:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, call her by her name while you knock.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.20,0:35:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you do it this time, Aigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.20,0:35:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.86,0:35:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Too scared, aincha?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.47,0:35:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, whatever. I'll do the knocking myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.24,0:35:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You three, better not run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.01,0:35:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.38,0:35:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hanako-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.22,0:35:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-san? Hanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.99,0:35:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, let's stop this...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.63,0:35:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.01,0:35:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's here! {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.74,0:35:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{no idea, could be "what are you doing"}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.91,0:35:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.15,0:35:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.88,0:35:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! It's stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.05,0:35:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why is this happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.02,0:36:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We must have angered Hanako-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.01,0:36:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! It's Aigo's fault! We shouldn't have made fun of Hanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.03,0:36:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Aigo did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.99,0:36:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? All I did was... {actually "you yourselves did ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.69,0:36:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going to happen now?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.37,0:36:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hanako-san is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.88,0:37:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.26,0:37:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it you three who summoned me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.45,0:37:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mi-Mina?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.03,0:37:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Minako is possessed by Hanako-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.96,0:37:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you treat me as a plaything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.31,0:37:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You three called me here for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.58,0:37:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So why don't I avail myself to playing with you, as per your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.83,0:37:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.60,0:37:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.60,0:37:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it hurts... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.20,0:38:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who called me, you selfish girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.98,0:38:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.01,0:38:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I teach you a fun game to play, you mortal thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.48,0:38:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.11,0:38:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise we won't call you anymore, please let Aigo go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.59,0:38:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're sorry! We're sorry! We won't do it again! Don't kill Aigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.63,0:38:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you leave me alone, to my peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.33,0:38:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.67,0:38:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.12,0:38:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes... I promise... I promise you!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.24,0:38:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.02,0:38:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.85,0:38:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.79,0:38:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.39,0:38:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.39,0:38:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{no idea}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.09,0:38:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.83,0:38:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.64,0:38:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina, are you feeling fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.50,0:39:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.89,0:39:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not forget your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.57,0:39:40.97,Song,,0,0,0,,In the cage, in the cage, \Na bird is being held...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.90,0:39:52.87,Sign,,0,0,0,,Red Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.30,0:41:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.67,0:41:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeda-sensei, Morita-kun is hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.11,0:41:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.87,0:41:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Morita-kun broke a beaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.91,0:41:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.34,0:41:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The red eyes... The red eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.54,0:41:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry him to the infirmary.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.62,0:41:36.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,Staff Room
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.04,0:41:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.19,0:41:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with all those wondering looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.86,0:41:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about Morita, he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.43,0:41:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.36,0:41:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Morita-kun's injury... Just like in that chemistry room legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.17,0:41:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That rumor of the spirits of the fallen haunting the chemistry room?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.81,0:41:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys seriously believe that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.34,0:41:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Everyone in class says,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.78,0:42:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,if you make eye contact with them, they'll punish you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.75,0:42:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Morita-kun said he saw red eyes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.35,0:42:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.19,0:42:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We live in the scientific age, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.79,0:42:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What are ghosts if not an invention of someone's fancy?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.26,0:42:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I gotta report for duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.90,0:42:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.80,0:42:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.73,0:42:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are all the boys? They are always so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.05,0:42:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.35,0:42:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when it's the boys who slack off, we're getting the shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.62,0:42:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we should hide and pull a prank on them when they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.52,0:42:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.99,0:42:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But this room is...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.19,0:42:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. Don't you wanna see the boys scared out of their wits?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.80,0:42:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.62,0:42:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.90,0:43:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,See? The atmosphere's just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.51,0:43:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't argue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.98,0:43:06.58,Sign,,0,0,0,,Preparation Room {準備室}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.85,0:43:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,An amazing find, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.99,0:43:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You good?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.96,0:43:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee! Don't scare us like that, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.23,0:43:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad. So, where should we put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.36,0:43:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right before the entrance should be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.60,0:43:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be sure to spook the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.14,0:43:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your worst, our smiling partner. {unsure but kaikatsu here seems to mean "cheerful/lively"}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.49,0:43:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he was a handsome guy before becoming a skeleton.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.43,0:43:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.78,0:43:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough fooling around. Let's hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.58,0:43:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.37,0:43:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? I'm getting the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.39,0:44:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aki, you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.94,0:44:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. It sure is scary in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.11,0:44:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the boys show up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.48,0:44:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.25,0:44:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.70,0:44:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.25,0:44:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.35,0:44:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,T-They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.69,0:44:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirits of the fallen!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.43,0:45:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure not to look them in the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.93,0:45:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.76,0:45:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeda-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.99,0:45:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.71,0:45:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,T-They really came to the chemistry room!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.73,0:45:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They came?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.50,0:45:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The spirits of the fallen did come!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.88,0:45:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We hid to prank the boys when they come, when suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.88,0:46:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Injured samurai with bright red eyes came!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.42,0:46:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you didn't look them in the eyes, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.04,0:46:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No way I'd ever look them in the eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.23,0:46:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We were so scared we kept our eyes shut all along! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.60,0:46:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.38,0:46:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't look them in the eyes, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.82,0:46:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't look them in the eyes, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.76,0:46:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.77,0:46:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just my imagination.
